query:
SELECT
                u.hashed_key AS "hashed_key!",
                (
                    SELECT
                        value
                    FROM
                        storage_logs
                    WHERE
                        hashed_key = u.hashed_key
                        AND miniblock_number <= $2
                    ORDER BY
                        miniblock_number DESC,
                        operation_number DESC
                    LIMIT
                        1
                ) AS "value?"
            FROM
                UNNEST($1 :: bytea []) AS u (hashed_key)
